name: Bimbo The Dog
description: FOR DECADES, BIMBO'S SILENT SUFFERING UNDER MICKEY'S CUNNING ANTICS REMAINED A HIDDEN CHAPTER. NOW, AS THE CURTAIN OF PROTECTION LIFTS IN THE PUBLIC DOMAIN, BIMBO EMERGES FROM THE SHADOWS. A TALE OF DECEPTION AND BETRAYAL UNFOLDS AS BIMBO, ARMED WITH THE FREEDOM TO TELL HIS SIDE, PLANS REVENGE.
